{"tid":380064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又益廢老）Uber加完價推長者優惠","createTime":"2017-08-29T22:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T00:09:53.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d57c102f07e7ea882965416961ba7196a1594fd","tid":380064,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:48:19.000Z","msg":"早前Uber大幅加價，旗下幾款車嘅最低車資加咗三至八成，轉過頭，佢哋就推出「UberSENIOR長者日」優惠喎。<br />\n<br />\nUber宣佈，由9月至12月，每個月1號嘅上午11點至下午4點，65歲或以上長者搭Uber可以每程平50蚊。<br />\n<br />\n香港區總經理佘雋知話，老人家近近哋出街飲茶，50蚊就夠晒cover車費，同一日最多有兩程優惠，仲啱啱夠來回㖭。"},{"pid":"776356a8c3a5faed0c4b4680c3e1baaf89f3f322","tid":380064,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:06:49.000Z","msg":"撘兩蚊巴士唔好<br />\n<br />\n又限日子又限時間"},{"pid":"f84e39df9b5afa0fdad0e293f685e5278224f799","tid":380064,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"加三至八成唔會考慮再搭👋🏻"},{"pid":"308fe0fed4d243ecf8b485f5748819b5a51628f2","tid":380064,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加三至八成唔會考慮再搭👋🏻</blockquote><br />\n短途撚先加者<br />\n長途撚除左5蚊預約費用無變過"},{"pid":"f505d831d1247550a1d77dd30fd205bd7b1b43b6","tid":380064,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加三至八成唔會考慮再搭👋🏻</blockquote><br />\n短途撚先加者<br />\n長途撚除左5蚊預約費用無變過</blockquote><br />\n證明好多人睇新聞淨係睇幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366d5ab6db0be0c94a51f95ff9cd8258e451e962","tid":380064,"uid":88252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:32:07.000Z","msg":"忍唔住賴係車到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa5476c4f8e759bdbb48332b7bb17159151b15c","tid":380064,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:57:55.000Z","msg":"識得用uber既老野都幾犀利下"},{"pid":"a4e47e4652859739dd4318a4b9ab9c6faf